org.gbif.mybatis.type

Class EnumDictTypeHandler<T extends Enum<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.mybatis.type.EnumDictTypeHandler<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the exact enumeration to convert
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.ibatis.type.TypeHandler<T>

    public class EnumDictTypeHandler<T extends Enum<?>>
extends Object
implements org.apache.ibatis.type.TypeHandler<T>
    General enumeration type handler that converts enums into their string name() representation and vice versa. Converting into the enum is case insensitive.
